{"tid":1589874,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣讀書後悔（多字慎入）","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T16:08:12.000Z","uid":325269,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd45fdb9d88a95f205cab7207c4068ed1df4b59","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"今年去咗台灣讀書，讀咗3個禮拜，但已經頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自問國語能力唔差，應付到日常，但一上到堂就好似聽𡁵外星話咁，啲中文terms，要諗好奈先勉強知道咩意思。而加冇一科追得上進度，我仲摸索𡁵。<br />\n<br />\n加上太掛住香港，日日將啲時間放係香港到， 但又做唔到啲乜，覺得好無力。諗住可以同學校嘅港人一齊圍爐，結果身邊嘅係港豬。而加日日返學就自閉，唔笑、唔同人講嘢，完全冇心情。<br />\n<br />\n讀過asso一年，sem1有3，sem2跌到得翻2。而加諗住讀返asso,由sem2讀起，想升返本地U，下年先可以報翻名。<br />\n<br />\n但唔知尼年點捱，有冇人可以比建議我，要屌我廢，隨便<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，利申香港冇住嘅地方，台灣學費同生活費自己一邊發夢一邊賺，嗰陣好彩有人免費借地方比我訓，好多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！如果知我邊個，唔好篤我出尼<br />\n<br />\n題外話，唔知係咪小弟樣衰，學校啲行政人員同醫生都閪我面，當然都有遇過好嘅人。<br />\n<br />\nPs.第一次開post,結構同用字有啲亂<br />\n<br />\n929個日台灣都會有遊行，如果你咁啱喺台灣，可以尼遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGWNZMb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGWNZMb.jpg&h=270bbcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港 時代革命<br />\n#五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n#我咃冇退路<br />\n#如果我哋向暴權暴柒屈服 我哋死去嘅手足係唔會原諒我哋<br />\n#Chinazi"},{"pid":"8289c08d7352675fd1a254a49de36f1d13c9b6f7","tid":1589874,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"8535f11f8291dc53818b959eae5a63a74c51bdb3","tid":1589874,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"識唔到台妹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3614245d326d9c331d204c12bc593d1257609556","tid":1589874,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"屌台妹"},{"pid":"f755d426200c2ed54b76be727e51161776ac0bd8","tid":1589874,"uid":96169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"主動啲識人啦<br />\n你都去左啦 番黎都唔一定好<br />\n係台灣都幫到手咖"},{"pid":"99ffffb8d204a8082c8639398935f5c234c2c309","tid":1589874,"uid":321784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"既然讀得唔開心，有冇諗過番香港。<br />\n<br />\n利申：諗住quit asso"},{"pid":"1daa8686085ae2a782183dc7182765c2cd8ed976","tid":1589874,"uid":55125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"我唔知你幾大 但比盡二字頭<br />\n讀書讀書 你有無諗過為咩而讀？<br />\n興趣？ 錢？ 避世？"},{"pid":"8de68bbda53ac6f39536d0283be8c8903c99f79b","tid":1589874,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"咩科咁慘，垃圾U定好U?<br />\n搵唔到有興趣讀嘅野，返黎香港驚你都係無限輪迴<br />\n可能只係將個希望放咗喺離開台灣=返香港<br />\n好好利用呢段時間explore下人生？"},{"pid":"cce79795ec8200532f643b78212a34e411ec9f25","tid":1589874,"uid":262674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"好難幫<br />\n自己努力啲追進度<br />\n<br />\n港豬唔緊要<br />\n當識下人<br />\n唔一定傾政治<br />\n可以傾閒計<br />\n<br />\n未必係樣衰<br />\n係個氣質問題<br />\n改變你對自己既諗法先"},{"pid":"03e07bcbce2ff7b447c6b304f1bbfc5e6c96ddef","tid":1589874,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"Gap一年返香港學下做台仔先<br />\n仲可以加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a6938c3b2d7baacda7b4c1ee5db971dca79abf","tid":1589874,"uid":142151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"［海外戰線］929台灣撐港大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589854</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0647dc2f97e9d11156718c32861004e2dd8a9a42","tid":1589874,"uid":259724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:56:27.000Z","msg":"真心可以試take gap year諗下自己想點走條路"},{"pid":"cde30f8be2ce648af086f9c4733cd2eea7bac730","tid":1589874,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:03:15.000Z","msg":"有啲人係唔啱讀書 <br />\n試下第二啲出路"},{"pid":"4cc076f5f9cee4f0a6429b173ab1bd45767ef643","tid":1589874,"uid":208402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"我台灣讀左一年quit左  返香港讀asso<br />\n完全同你相反  覺得台灣讀書太hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf32a3eed1df722e3e83bcdb973898ae740c710","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8535f11f8291dc53818b959eae5a63a74c51bdb3","tid":1589874,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"識唔到台妹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"中意香港女仔多啲（有發夢嗰啲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e355224bd6ccd3dfe3b57b76e4b71561fd7e71","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99ffffb8d204a8082c8639398935f5c234c2c309","tid":1589874,"uid":321784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"既然讀得唔開心，有冇諗過番香港。<br />\n<br />\n利申：諗住quit asso"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"有吖，但下年先報返asso，ching點解想quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce47bac10662665285a095201ddd57558e83012c","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1daa8686085ae2a782183dc7182765c2cd8ed976","tid":1589874,"uid":55125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:53:17.000Z","msg":"我唔知你幾大 但比盡二字頭<br />\n讀書讀書 你有無諗過為咩而讀？<br />\n興趣？ 錢？ 避世？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"有吖，為前途同夢想，年頭已經plan去台灣讀書，再藉台灣跳去外國進修。但經歷咗3個月運動，突然想留翻喺香港，但最後太遲，得翻後備位，所以冇報到，照去咗台灣"},{"pid":"a65a673b8bd0e89f2243dfd68ac89d5f11c8f062","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de68bbda53ac6f39536d0283be8c8903c99f79b","tid":1589874,"uid":36673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"咩科咁慘，垃圾U定好U?<br />\n搵唔到有興趣讀嘅野，返黎香港驚你都係無限輪迴<br />\n可能只係將個希望放咗喺離開台灣=返香港<br />\n好好利用呢段時間explore下人生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"其實又唔關科事，我唔知間學校算唔算好。因為係啲國語教育好難聽得明（對我而言）。加上個心放咗喺香港到，所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35bcd822fd5db9560ae7b07005afe22df9a3ae1","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cc076f5f9cee4f0a6429b173ab1bd45767ef643","tid":1589874,"uid":208402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"我台灣讀左一年quit左  返香港讀asso<br />\n完全同你相反  覺得台灣讀書太hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"初時我都有咁嘅諗法，但我個班好唔同，啲人勤力到一個點。。。但有一科個老師就冇備課咁上堂囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0787529e98a84f45566d3459d21d01d39cede62","tid":1589874,"uid":147871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a3bc5f0a6f65c65513ee5c6e5b7d75a07795a7","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e07bcbce2ff7b447c6b304f1bbfc5e6c96ddef","tid":1589874,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"Gap一年返香港學下做台仔先<br />\n仲可以加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"返香港就唔會再返台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05099d38d7eaeb0dc7d03ed8523c2551c269a03f","tid":1589874,"uid":28252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23a3bc5f0a6f65c65513ee5c6e5b7d75a07795a7","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e07bcbce2ff7b447c6b304f1bbfc5e6c96ddef","tid":1589874,"uid":28252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:54:26.000Z","msg":"Gap一年返香港學下做台仔先<br />\n仲可以加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"返香港就唔會再返台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:38:55.000Z","msg":"屌你啦，咁咪撚讀書<br />\nquit左做野比讀書更有價值啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3563135231fff46a77293bca50789cadf16bf9a","tid":1589874,"uid":319458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"出得去讀書就一定係咁架喇<br />\n三年幾前我岩岩去到日本個時都係咁<br />\n以為去到日本就可以好似上左天堂咁啦<br />\n點知勁撚唔習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一星期左右就想番香港 <br />\n但諗下用左幾多時間做準備工夫只好死頂落去<br />\n都頂左幾年 仲差一年幾要頂落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油啦手足<br />\n識下新朋友 星期六日去遠少少玩 時間好快過<br />\n仲有台灣飛香港好平 大時大節都可以飛番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f4f689863232c90272700b0e8ff53135d512ab","tid":1589874,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05099